reviews.review_text:
Excellent Pre-FM Board Lotsa Jerry full out and high in the mix.

Neat-o clarification job on the part of Mr Jay Ashley thanks to Mr Gary Field.

And the Archives.

Thank yous all around.

I think this is my widely distributed recording I taped this on a cheap Ampeg or Teac cassette deck from the FM broadcast on WIOQ or WMMR in Philly from the live broacast. I believe this is a copy. It was traded heavily at the time.
Tom Dewey
